其中，「A1B」幾個字母與數字分別代表：<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bechtel.com/assets/files/PDF/brief1202.pdf |format=PDF |title=Bechtel Briefs -- December 2002 |accessdate=2007-09-19 |archive-date=2008-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080720060236/http://www.bechtel.com/assets/files/PDF/brief1202.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* A：航空母舰（Aircraft carrier）
* 1：由負責合約承包商設計的第一代-{zh-cn:核反应堆堆芯; zh-hk:核反應堆堆心; zh-tw:核反應器爐心;}-
* B：該反應爐的合約承包商為[[貝泰船用推進公司|貝泰船用推進公司]]（Bechtel Marine Propulsion Corporation）

唯一使用此反應爐的軍艦是[[福特級核動力航空母艦|福特級核動力航空母艦]]。每艘航母有2個反應爐，每個A1B反應爐熱功率估計為700[[百萬瓦|MW]]，較上一代[[A4W反應爐|A4W反應爐]]增加25%，並預計發電及推力系統有較高的運作效率。每個反應爐推算可產生125[[百萬瓦|MW]]電力。<ref>{{Cite news|url= http://www.world-nuclear.org/information-library/non-power-nuclear-applications/transport/nuclear-powered-ships.aspx|title= Nuclear-Powered Ships: Nuclear Propulsion Systems|date= May 22, 2017|work= |newspaper= World Nuclear Association|access-date= |via= |archive-date= 2020-06-22|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200622213526/https://www.world-nuclear.org/Information-Library/Non-power-nuclear-applications/Transport/Nuclear-Powered-Ships.aspx|dead-url= no}}</ref> 根據A4W反應爐的資料推算<ref>{{cite web
